doc:
Provides a mutable reference to the element at the given index.

Element at index 0 is the front of the queue.

# Examples

```
use std::collections::VecDeque;

let mut buf = VecDeque::new();
buf.push_back(3);
buf.push_back(4);
buf.push_back(5);
buf.push_back(6);
assert_eq!(buf[1], 4);
if let Some(elem) = buf.get_mut(1) {
    *elem = 7;
}
assert_eq!(buf[1], 7);
```
